channel.title: The Da Vinci Code
channel.desc: Action, Drama, Thriller, Mystery 2006 Robert Langdon is determined to solve the mystery of a corpse found in the Louvre. Deciphering the symbols carved on its body, he uncovers a secret, thousand-year-old society whose truth threatens the foundations of Western civilization. Tom Hanks, Audrey Tautou, Jean Reno, Ian McKellen, Paul Bettany, Ron Howard, Akiva Goldsman, Dan Brown, Paul Bettany, Alfred Molina, Jurgen Prochnow.
